STATE of North Carolina
v.
George Elton HINNANT. No. 22A99-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 6, 2004. George Elton Hinnant, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 23rd day of July 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Wake County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of October 2004."
